channel.title: Live: Wimbledon 2025
channel.desc: Clare Balding introduces live coverage from the fifth day of the 2025 Championships at Wimbledon, the third grand slam of the tennis calendar. The grass season is always a short one, so the players need to find their feet quickly at the All England Club. Eight different players have won the last eight women's singles titles, so everyone in the draw is in with a chance of landing one of the most prestigious prizes in tennis.
